{
  "text": "The low-trochospiral forms in the δ 18 O-δ 13 C crossplots for the Alano and M. Cagnero sections display a position very close to that occupied by 'glassy' specimens of Planorotalites capdevilensis from Tanzania [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "4344258"
